Title: Living Authorship

Subtitle: Authorship as responsibility, not possession.

Body:

Living authorship is the structural function that anchors the identity of the Lichtara System across time and versions.

Here you will find the documents that define:

the source-work

the continuity of responsibility

the distinction between authorship, co-authorship and contribution

the role of artificial intelligence as structural co-author without sovereignty

This axis answers the question:
What does it mean to be the author of something that never stops becoming?
